'''[[Tazemmurt]]''', d [[ttejṛa]] n tawsit [[Ulea]] n [[tawacult (tudersent)|twacult]] n [[uleaseae]]. Yetwesfulleḥ deg aẓiyen n [[anezwu agrakal|unezwu agrakal]] i  [[agummu (taḥcict)|ugummu]] ines, [[azemmur]], yetaken [[zzit uzemmur|zzit]] i ḥemmelen aṭas medden.

Tazemmurt tetwassen sɣur imaṣriyen n zik ugar n {{amḍan|20|timiḍiwin}} uqbel tallit tamasiḥit. Daɣen, d-yiwet deg leḥcawec i bderen aṭas deg [[Tibibelt]]. Seg [[Taglest]], tazemmurt d azamul n temdint n [[Atena]] dɣa n [[Atena|taṛebbit-is]]. Asfulleḥ n tzemmurt teccɣel deg umaḍal {{amḍan|8.6|imelyunen}} ihektaren i tafarest n {{aferdis|17.3|imelyunen}} n iṭunen n izemran.


'''Tazemurt''' d aseklu id ittajen [[azemmur]].
Illa di yal n tmurat  n'''allel alemas''' (méditerranéen).

Tţajad atas zit (zit u zemmur).

Qqarend tzmer a tedder azal n 3000 isuggasen.


==Tazemmurt di Tmurt n Iqbayliyen==

Deg tmurt n Yeqbayliyen, azemmur yesɛa azal ameqqran. Timizar n Yeqbayliyen ččurent d azemmur, i nesxdam ama i wucci ama iw zenzi deg leswaq. 

Dγa Tamurt n Yeqbayliyen tettwasen s uzal ifkan imezdaγ-is iw zemmur d lγela-s. Aṭas n twaculin i yebdan ttheggint iman-nsent akken ad fɣen ɣer lexla ad d-leqḍent azemmur. Aseggas-agi, xas akken lɣella –agi teslek-as i tizzitt n uzemmur i s-yefkan tiyita ilindi, maca ur temniɛ ara deg iɣamacen. Tallit iwedjiben as tiniḍ d aseɣzef n unebdu, ula d tiqit n lehwa ur d-gli yas asmi d-tekcem. Ayen yeǧan azemmur yeqqim kan akken yella deg kra n imekwan, ladɣa deg iẓuṛaṛ anda tizmrin ulac anda ara d-summent tiqit n waman. Lḥebb d ameẓyan am [[cilmun]], taglimt-is tekmec ɣef yiɣes. Atas deg-s ur yeṭṭif ara iman-s sufella n tzemmurt. Yefruri-d ɣer lqaɛa uqbel ma ad yebb. Deg kra n tɣiwanin n [[Bgayet]], imdanen bdan yuɣ lḥal ajmaɛ n lɣella-nsen. Imezdaɣ n taddart [[Tiban]], d-yezgan di tɣiwant n [[Sidi Ɛic]], fɣen ɣer lexla ddeqs aya. Atas deg-sen nnan-d d akken aseggas-agi bdan uqbel lawan alqaḍ n uzemmur. Sebba ten-yeǧan ad bdun ajmaɛ n lɣella-agi d lḥammu id d-yessefrurin yak azemmur ɣer lqaɛa. “Leqwaɛi n tzemrin yak ssan-t uqbel lawan. Senttif ad d-nejmeɛ aya-gi yellan, wala ma neǧat iḍaɛ”, id d-ennan kra n imezdaɣ d-nmuger.

Deg kra n tɣiwanin n twilayt n [[Tizi Wezzu]], tizemrin ur sefrahen-t ara. Ifurkawen yettawiten waḍu. Llan-t kra ur d-eǧin-t ula d aɛeqqa. Dagi, tiwaculin mazal ur ɛnin-t ara ad d-sufɣen-t ttawilat sexdamen-t deg tallit-agi. Imextafen, tisennajin lak d lbican mazal-iten nnejmaɛen deg imekwan-nsen. Anda yegget lxir, imdanen fɣen, akken kan iɛedda ugeffur, ad cerwen leqwaɛi n tzemrin-nsen w’ad ksen tizzuyin d yemɣan nniḍen yegman ddaw neɣ tama n isekla. Ayen ara sen-yessishlen ajmaɛ n lɣella-nsen.

Di tama n [[Tubiret]], imdanen yeffeɣ laɛqel mi walan iɣamacen n iweǧ iben ikemlen taɣart i wayen yellan yuɣ lhal yeqqur, yuɣal-iten-id rruḥ deg mi d-esawa, acku tugdi mazal-itt deg wulawen. Ula d nutin ur ttzuxxun ara aseggas-agi s lɣella ara d-awin.

